des:
My Rock is YOUR Rock. All of your favorite rock artists from AC/DC, Led Zeppelin, Jimi Hendrix, The Rolling Stone and Aerosmith to Nirvana, Pearl Jam, Green Day, Guns N Roses, Metallica and more!

Whether you grew up listening to the classics of the 60's, 70's and 80's, cranked up the grunge and alternative songs of the 90's or prefer the best rock music of the 2000's to today - if it rocks, it plays here.

Listen to more stations at rudyparachoniak.com.
